Source: pt-os-core
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Maintainer: pi-top <deb-maintainers@pi-top.com>
Build-Depends:
 debhelper-compat (= 12),
Standards-Version: 4.5.1
Homepage: https://pi-top.com/

Package: pt-os
Architecture: all
Depends:
 ${misc:Depends},
 pt-os-sys-mods,
Recommends:
# 'pt-os-core' packages
 pt-os-apps,
 pt-os-dev-tools,
 pt-device-support,
 pt-os-net-mods,
 pt-os-ui,
 pt-os-user-libs,
# systemd services
 pt-os-notify-services,
# Required for ssh login motd (see OS build)
 neofetch,
# Only suggested by device manager to support headless configurations
 xprintidle,
Description: pi-topOS top-level dummy package
 The root package of pi-topOS modifications to Raspberry Pi OS.

Package: pt-os-init
Architecture: all
Depends:
 ${misc:Depends},
Description: pi-topOS init script
 This package handles all initialisation of pi-topOS, such as configuring for
 onboarding/desktop.

Package: pt-os-version
Architecture: all
Depends:
 ${misc:Depends},
Description: pi-topOS version file
 This package provides an easy-to-parse text file providing the current pi-topOS
 version.

Package: pt-os-apps
Architecture: all
Depends:
 ${misc:Depends}
Recommends:
# Disk Usage Analyzer
 baobab,
# Keyboard and mouse sharing
 barrier,
# Keep display alive
 caffeine,
 chromium-browser,
# VS Code
 code,
 gimp,
# Multi-touch friendly calculator
 gnome-calculator,
 htop,
 libreoffice-pi,
 libreoffice-common,
 imagemagick,
 mtpaint,
 mu-editor,
 python3-minecraftpi,
 realvnc-vnc-viewer,
 scratch3,
 smartsim,
 sonic-pi,
 touche,
 vlc,
Description: pi-topOS Applications
 This package contains the files and dependencies required
 to install and configure pi-topOS' GUI applications.

Package: pt-os-dev-tools
Architecture: all
Depends:
 ${misc:Depends},
Recommends:
 asciinema,
 debtree,
 graphviz,
 p7zip-full,
 silversearcher-ag,
 squashfs-tools,
 tree,
 vim,
 zip,
 zsh,
Description: pi-topOS Development Support
 This metapackage contains the files and dependencies required
 to install and configure pi-topOS' development-related
 components. This includes scripts that are used as part of the OS
 build pipeline.

Package: pt-device-support
Architecture: all
Depends:
 ${misc:Depends},
 pt-device-manager,
 python3-pitop,
# Additional hardware support
 pt-display-port,
 pt-miniscreen,
# Software updaters
 pt-firmware-updater,
 pt-touchscreen,
# Recommend screen blanking dependency
# (only suggested by device manager to support headless configurations)
 xprintidle,
Description: pi-top Device Support
 This metapackage contains dependencies required to install and configure
 low-level device-related components for using pi-top hardware.

Package: pt-os-ui
Architecture: all
Depends:
 ${misc:Depends},
 autorandr,
 pt-os-bootsplash,
 pt-os-ui-mods,
 pt-os-web-portal-desktop,
Description: pi-topOS UI
 This metapackage contains the files and dependencies required
 to install and configure pi-topOS' UI-related components.

Package: pt-os-user-libs
Architecture: all
Depends:
 ${misc:Depends},
# pi-top Python SDK + all dependencies
 python3-pitop-full,
Recommends:
# Useful for graphing
 python3-matplotlib,
# Sonic Pi with Python
 python3-sonic,
Description: pi-topOS User Libraries
 This metapackage contains optional libraries (primarily Python) for pi-topOS.

Package: pt-os-notifications
Architecture: all
Depends:
 ${misc:Depends},
 xfce4-notifyd,
 notify-send-ng,
Suggests:
 pt-os-ui-mods,
Description: pi-top Desktop Notification Service
 Interface for showing notifications directly to the user at the desktop.
 Handles detecting which display to target, as well as which user is
 using the display. This service wraps around notify-send.sh to provide
 advanced notification management.
